  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Building Crush! is a puzzle game where you play the role of a demolitions expert and try to bring down buildings faster than your opponent. Place bombs in windowed blocks to clear connected blocks of the same color, and make chains with the falling blocks that match up. There are several bomb power-ups to increase their effectiveness, as well as assist characters to hinder your opponent. You can play against the CPU or a friend.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "Building Crush yours is one!\n\nLearn Crush road building and fighting our rivals!!\n\nI'll work after the rice is good!!\n\nBuilding Crush! is about taking control of a demolition man that have to destroy a building before the opponent do it.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb_storyline"
    }
